\f0\fs24 \cf0 Morphological feedback\ \pard\pardeftab709\ri0\sl200\ql\qnatural
\fs12 \cf0 The feedback messages are determined by the combination of morphological features in the lexicon and the inflection task at hand. The morphological specification below gives a rule stating that there is a vowel change in illative singular for bisyllabic nouns that end with the vowel \i i \i0 . The corresponding feedback message instructs the user to remember the vowel change.\ \ }

